{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all restaurants and takeaways to offer half or small portions ",
        "additional_details": "We believe giving people the option of still eating out but not having to order more than they need will be beneficial.",
        "background": "In a bid to tackle obesity, we would like the Government to make it a legal requirement for restaurants and takeaways to provide half or small portions of all meal options on menus. We would like these to have a reduced price too. ",
